eza (a), that reciting YAA MUQEE-TO 7 times and blowing on rainwater and if it is given to an ill-mannered child, will become well-mannered and a dull intellect child will become intelligent.", "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": "Hazrat Imam Reza (a) se manqool hai keh YAA MUQEE-TO 7 martaba baarish ke paani par dam (blow) kar ke bad-akhlaaq bachche ko peela diya jaaye to woh khoos khwa ho jaayega aur kund zahen (kam dimaagi) bachcha zahin o fitteen (hosiyaar) ho jaayega.", "UrduDescription": "حضرت امام رضاؑ سے منقول ہے کہ ’’یَامُقِیْتُ‘‘ 7 بار بارش کے پانی پر دم کرکے بد اخلاق بچے کو پلا دیا تو وہ خوش خو ہوجائے گا اورکند ذہن بچہ ذہین و فطین ہوجائے گا۔ ", "English": null, "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": null, "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRed